Note that mail to anyone@users.sourceforge.net no longer works.
You have to log in and send a private message which is then
forwarded to their email proper.

sox_ng is currently maintained by

	Martin Guy		martinwguy at gmail.com

and the second keyholder to sox_ng is Reuben Thomas.

